---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';

const title = 'Beauty & Cosmetics Fulfillment | Temperature Control 18-22°C, Fragile Glass, 99.9% Quality | MTP';
const description = 'Specialized fulfillment for cosmetics, perfumes, serums, skincare. Climate control 18-22°C, anti-fragile glass protection, UV-light dark storage, 99.9% quality control, 100% insurance, 24-hour delivery.';
const ogImage = 'https://profm.ua/images/fulfillment-beauty.jpg';

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Service',
  name: title,
  description: description,
  provider: {
    '@type': 'Organization',
    name: 'MTP Group',
    url: 'https://profm.ua/en/'
  },
  areaServed: {
    '@type': 'Country',
    name: 'UA'
  },
  priceRange: '₴50-₴150'
};
---

<Base title={title} description={description} ogImage={ogImage} lang="en">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-500 text-white py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
        Beauty &amp; Cosmetics Fulfillment<br />Temperature Stable, 99.9% Quality, Fragile Protection
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-95 leading-relaxed">
        Perfumes, serums, oils, creams in glass flasks. Climate control 18-22°C, dark UV-protected storage, anti-fragile packaging, sterile hygiene handling, 99.9% quality control, 100% insurance, 24-hour delivery.
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-red-600 px-8 py-4 rounded font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
        Start Beauty Fulfillment
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Why Beauty &amp; Cosmetics Require Special Care</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🌡️ Temperature Stability</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Perfumes, oils, serums degrade above 25°C. Ingredients separate and lose efficacy. Requires strict 18-22°C control. One temperature spike = product ruined and unsellable.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">💧 Humidity &amp; Light Sensitivity</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Cosmetics degrade from moisture and direct sunlight. Requires dark, dry storage below 60% humidity. UV light exposure = oxidized, discolored, degraded formula within hours.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🍾 Fragile Glass Flask Packaging</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Perfumes in glass vials, creams in glass jars. Single crack = 100% product loss. Requires maximum protective padding during storage and transit. Glass containers are breakage risk.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">✨ Hygiene &amp; Purity</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Cosmetics ultra-sensitive to contamination. Single hair in cream = 1-star review. Requires sterile handling: staff in gowns, masks, gloves. Daily sanitization of all surfaces.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

\1  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">How MTP Group Handles Cosmetics & Beauty Orders</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-12">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          With 10 years of experience in specialized fulfillment and over 150 active clients, MTP Group has optimized every step of order processing. Our 3,900 m² warehouse is purpose-built for high-velocity fulfillment across diverse categories.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Fulfillment Challenge</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Beauty product fulfillment requires precision: wrong shade of foundation ruins customer satisfaction. Orders typically contain 3–8 items (foundation + concealer + powder + brush + skincare). Returns and exchanges are expensive.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          MTP Group's approach: Every cosmetic is labeled by shade, brand, and size. Our warehouse uses barcode scanning for 100% SKU verification. Pick accuracy is <strong>99.95%</strong> because wrong concealer shade = automatic return. Staff are trained to recognize product variations. 3–4 minute average picking time maintains speed without sacrificing accuracy.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Why Retailers Choose MTP</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Cosmetics margins are 40–50% but breakage and returns reduce actual profit by 8–12%. Incorrect picks result in ₴200–500 refund costs. Our damage-free packing and 99.95% accuracy protect your margin.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          MTP Group has processed <strong>22,000+ cosmetics orders processed, 45+ beauty retailers served</strong>. Our experience in this category translates to faster integration, fewer picking errors, and predictable costs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

   Beauty &amp; Cosmetics Services</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🌡️ Climate Control 18-22°C</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Dedicated temperature-stable zone. Hourly sensor monitoring with alerts for any deviation. Hourly documentation and compliance logging. Backup power for continuous climate control.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🏭 Sterile Hygiene Handling</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Staff in sterile gowns, masks, gloves, caps. Daily warehouse sanitization protocol. Bacteriostatic container treatment. Highest hygiene standards for product purity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">📦 Anti-Fragile Glass Protection</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Glass flasks wrapped in air cushioning, placed in protective cardboard boxes, then shipped in secondary protective outer box. Multi-layer shock absorption. Maximum damage prevention.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🔍 100% Quality Control 99.9%</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Zero-defect QC: every item inspected (not 10% sampling). Seal integrity, appearance, smell, consistency, temperature at packing verified. Only perfect items ship.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Pricing for Beauty &amp; Cosmetics</h2>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border border-gray-200 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">Picking, Climate Storage, Delivery</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Picking per order</span>
            <span class="font-bold">20–30 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>100% quality control inspection</span>
            <span class="font-bold">Included</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Climate-controlled storage</span>
            <span class="font-bold">+25 UAH/pallet/mo</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Standard delivery</span>
            <span class="font-bold">50–150 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>100% insurance coverage</span>
            <span class="font-bold">Included</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
        <h3 class="font-bold mb-3">Example: Cosmetics Store on Rozetka FBO (400 orders/month)</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Picking: 400 × 25 = 10,000 UAH<br/>
          Climate storage: 1 pallet × 425 = 425 UAH/month<br/>
          Delivery across Ukraine: 400 × 100 = 40,000 UAH<br/>
          <strong class="text-lg">TOTAL: 50,425 UAH/month = 126 UAH per order</strong><br/>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Includes: temperature control, 99.9% quality, 100% insurance, sterile hygiene, fragile protection</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Quality Guarantees</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">99.9%</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Quality Control</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Zero-defect: every item 100% inspected</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">18-22°C</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Stable Temperature</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Hourly monitoring with automatic alerts</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">&lt;0.5%</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Breakage Rate</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Multi-layer protective glass packaging</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Why Fulfillment Speed & Accuracy Matter for Your Business</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">⏱️ Speed = Competitive Advantage</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">E-commerce customers expect 24-48 hour delivery. Slow fulfillment leads to lost orders and negative reviews. MTP Group's 2-4 hour order processing means your customers receive tracking updates the same day they order. This builds trust and encourages repeat purchases. Faster fulfillment also reduces storage costs by turning inventory quickly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">✅ Accuracy = Customer Retention</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Wrong item? The customer will return it, costing you both labor and shipping. Wrong quantity? Dispute and potential chargeback. Our 99.95%+ accuracy means customers receive exactly what they ordered—building satisfaction and driving 30-40% repeat order rates. Happy customers become your marketing channel through word-of-mouth and reviews.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">💰 Margins Are Everything</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Fulfillment is often 10-20% of your total order cost. Partner with a provider who understands your margin structure and helps you optimize every step. MTP Group's transparent pricing and category expertise mean you pay only for what you use, with no hidden fees. Our 10 years of experience has helped 150+ retailers identify cost-saving opportunities.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🔄 Scaling Without Stress</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Black Friday. Holiday season. New product launch. These peak periods either make or break your year. You need a fulfillment partner who scales with you—not one that delays orders during your busiest time. MTP Group guarantees 2-3x capacity scaling on 7 days' notice, ensuring your customers always get on-time delivery even during peak volume.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-500 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Perfect Your Beauty Fulfillment?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">
        Climate control, 99.9% quality, sterile hygiene, fragile protection, 100% insurance. Start today.
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-red-600 px-8 py-4 rounded font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
        Request a Quote
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)}></script>
</Base>
